title: Patrick Mahomes, LeBron James, playoffs, Baker Mayfield, Sam Darnold
itunes:title: Patrick Mahomes, LeBron James, playoffs, Baker Mayfield, Sam Darnold
description:
Colin discusses athletes like Patrick Mahomes and LeBron James doing what politicians can't, players not delivering in the playoffs, Baker Mayfield being the main problem for the Browns, and why people don't give Sam Darnold the credit he deserves. Guests include Antonio Daniels, Bryan Cox, Rob Parker, and Dwight Freeney.
